    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those looking for a functional car without the premium price of a newer model. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few months. It's a solid, honest car that gets the job done despite its cosmetic imperfections.",
