    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of age and use. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that is beginning to feel soft. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it back to its former glory.",
