    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a concours-level standard. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a machine in pristine, showroom condition, entirely free from mechanical or aesthetic compromise. Its provenance is documented, and its presentation remains unrivaled. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as the definitive choice in the current market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
